-content/uploads/2022/05/0523-4a-694x532.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="532" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/0523-4a-694x532.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/0523-4a-1174x900.jpg 1174w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/0523-4a-768x589.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/0523-4a.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>從預告短片展示的拍攝效果看來，跟 BetaFPV 飛行器的拍攝能力相當類似，有外國網站估計 Insta360 將會發表搭配自家相機使用的飛行器，或者直接推出有全景拍攝功能的航拍機產品。</p><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://petapixel.com/2022/05/21/insta360-teases-something-that-looks-like-a-drone/">petapixel</a></p><p>unwire.hk Mewe 專頁：<a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"> https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;autohide=1&amp;theme=light&amp;color=white&amp;controls=0&amp;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><div class="feedflare">
